unEdit

public java.util.Map<Node,Node> unEdit(MutableGraph mg)
Undo a filterizer edit by generating new nodes and edges. A topologic copy of the edited subgraph is added to mg. The new nodes may not be equal to the filtered nodes, but it is guranteed that for each filtered node there is one topologically identical node created. The mapping from the filtered nodes to the new nodes is returned.

Parameters:
mg - a mutable graph to edit.
Returns:
a mapping from the old filtered nodes to the new nodes.
